snippet.title: Tightened Thrice (GTA 3) - V1.0 Release Trailer
snippet.description:
'Tightened Thrice' is a 'Tightened Vice' prequel mod for GTA 3 that seeks to make every single mission in the game harder, with a focus on ruining the muscle memory of speedrunners...

Download/details: https://gtaforums.com/topic/989421-tightened-thrice/
